    <item>
      <title>波洛兹听取有关将加拿大养老金管理人员拉回国内的新基金提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poloz-hears-proposals-for-new-fund-to-pull-canada-s-pension-managers-back-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行前行长史蒂芬波洛兹 (Stephen Poloz) 正在研究一系列让加拿大养老基金更多地投资国内经济的想法，其中包括创建一个共同基金，使部分养老基金更容易达成交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poloz-hears-proposals-for-new-fund-to-pull-canada-s-pension-managers-back-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 14:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非联合政府股价上涨刺激财富增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-africa-household-wealth-rises-to-highest-level-in-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非央行表示，第二季度南非家庭财富增加，因为其资产市值的增幅超过了负债的增幅，部分原因是股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-africa-household-wealth-rises-to-highest-level-in-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特和利比亚有望增加石油供应，油价继续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，沙特阿拉伯承诺在 12 月份增加产量，而利比亚任命了新央行行长，为恢复部分原油生产铺平了道路，导致油价连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
